  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">RECLAIM Sustainability! Europe - Gold</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project aims to ensure:
-Gold sourcing companies in Europe commit to and implement responsible sourcing practices for ASM gold and invest in the development of a responsible ASM sector.
-Partnerships with other CSOs and networks advocating for improvements in the ASM sector regarding decent work, fair value distribution and sustainable natural resources management.
-Public sector adopts and implements regulatory frameworks that are ASM inclusive and address decent work, fair value distribution and sustainable natural resources management in international supply chains for gold.</narrative>
  </description>
